entry.title: High Hutch - Luxury Smoking Accessory Stash Box
entry.summary:
Vendor: High Hutch
Type: Baggies | Jars
Price: 110.00

Our sleek matte black bamboo rolling tray design is magnetized conveniently to the lid of stash box! 
The scraper is magnetized on the tray for secure and safe storage. 

The High Hutch 4 piece aluminum grinder comes with a large catch for maximum flower hold. Our strong magnetic lid reduces spill and keeps your herb secure. Grind up the most dense herb with the sharp teeth that perfectly grinds every bit in minimal twists. The stainless mesh pollen collector grabs all fine powders. Our smooth grip is comfortable and strong for effortless grinding! It comes with a scraper that simplifies collecting and removing the remaining pollen from the grinder. Aircraft anodized aluminum construction for required durability and long lasting use. Made with the highest quality of standards.  

The multipurpose metal ashtray/rolling tray is printed with the High Hutch logo to match the accessories in a visually appealing set. The tray is the perfect size to fit in the box. 

Going out? The matte black bamboo one hitter has a matching dugout and aluminum bat with an easy self cleaning push tip! Just grind up your flower, fill up the dugout and enjoy anywhere!

The aluminum black pollen press has no cheap plastic dowels! The threading on the press can handle high levels of pressure and will not strip under stress. All you need is your hand to use our press, no other tools involved! It can press your hard saved pollen into delightful pucks. 

The High Hutch comes with two smell proof, UV containers. It keeps your herbs fresh and protects them. Have confidence knowing the smell proof design locks in all scents and smells. Our discrete jars protect privacy and are made with high quality and durable glass. 

A matte black padlock and keys to finalize the box and keep your stash safe. 

All items are secured in a black padded insert, to prevent damage and keep your stash organized.
